{"tid":1451203,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人醒下啦","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:36:04.000Z","uid":272345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"138fc0bdd42d05eaa1655e3cb63504a973d91768","tid":1451203,"uid":272345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:31:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做唔到勇武既人<br />\n有人為我地冇左隻眼<br />\n有人為我地中左無限咁多槍<br />\n有人為我地付上青春被捕<br />\n有人為我地流血受傷<br />\n我地連罷工都驚？驚冇左份工？驚冇錢食飯？驚冇錢供樓？<br />\n係咁大家唔配有自由同民主<br />\n12/8 1pm 機場見<br />\n離境大堂 不見不散 黑警還眼</span>"},{"pid":"ba82c91b5f8c7504b4cf0a5ef824e4274cae4611","tid":1451203,"uid":11698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:33:06.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家 準備長期作戰<br />\n聽日唔好再玩接機 笑笑口和理非<br />\n記住個女仔半邊面係血既樣<br />\n記住班黑警1m距離內開槍+掉人落電梯<br />\n記住依家有幾嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日12/8 Full gear塞爆+癱瘓 成個機場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔唱歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔接機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔衝禁區<br />\n<br />\n保持憤怒 統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeffaeec270303809669808ac214d30273500c76","tid":1451203,"uid":272345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:34:20.000Z","msg":"黑警還眼"},{"pid":"4e05eb2b94c34bd9b2db53f250748bee40102e7c","tid":1451203,"uid":272345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:34:31.000Z","msg":"黑警還眼"},{"pid":"c535fa3090f45e005e6e147358cf01fff49c42de","tid":1451203,"uid":272345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:34:42.000Z","msg":"黑警還眼"},{"pid":"48393515a3